article_title: Hard Data On Trouble You'll Have Finding Doctors In Obamacare

article_metadata.description: The graph below illustrates data we developed on the doctor networks found in the Obamacare health plans versus comparable private health plans. The black text illustrates the average number of specialist doctors found in private health plans. The red text shows how many fewer doctors are found in the Obamacare plans [...]
article_metadata.author: Scott Gottlieb
